| !Run file for HUProlog
| by Justin Fletcher (20 Nov 1996)
| based on file by Andrew Wenn 8/5/91

UnSet HUPro$Dir
Run <Obey$Dir>.!Boot
|
|
| Requires C library version 3.50 or better
RMEnsure SharedCLibrary 3.50 If "<System$Path>" = "" Then Error 0 System resources cannot be found
RMEnsure SharedCLibrary 3.50 RMLoad System:modules.CLib
|
Unset HUPro$File
If "%0" <> "" Then Set HUPro$File -l %*0
|
| We require quite a bit of space, and 640k is the minimum
if "<Wimp$State>" = "desktop" Then TaskWindow "/|<HUPro$Dir>.Prolog <HUPro$File>" -quit -name Prolog -wimpslot 640k else /|<HUPro$Dir>.Prolog <HUPro$File>
